title: Trump OnlyFans with Ti Ti Jerry & Tampa Tony | Chris Distefano Presents: Chrissy Chaos | EP 75
description:
WELCOME to Chrissy Chaos! 
 
Chrissy CHAOS is live on the 4th of July from a backyard BBQ. Chris tries pork! Chris is joined by Ti Ti Jerry and his father Tampa Tony. Ti Ti breaks down the R Kelly case. What is federal prison? Ti Ti is excited for her boyfriend to get out of prison. Whats a first date after serving time like? Ti Ti wants to go on a cruise. Chris wants to take viagra for the patreon. Chris wants Tampa Tony to get ripped for his 75th birthday. What's your reason for living? How do we get gas prices down!? Joe Biden vs Trump in penis size? WHO YOU GOT?! NYC is not safe these days. Worst thing you ever did out of passion. Tampa Tony wants to fix America. Chris talks gender. Chris goes anti-basement! Chris breaks out some dance moves. We answer some Patreon questions!!! FULL CHAOS!
 
Remember to rate us on iTunes and Join our Patreon for a WEEKLY bonus ep!
